@BankingApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### List all accounts
GET {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a bank account
POST {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerName": "Alice Dupont",
  "ownerId": "user-001",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "initialBalance": 1000.00
}

###

### Get account by ID  (replace <id> with a real account GUID)
# @name account
GET {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/<id>
Accept: application/json

###

### Get account balance
GET {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/<id>/balance
Accept: application/json

###

### Update account
PUT {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerName": "Alice Martin"
}

###

### Close account
DELETE {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/<id>

###

### List all cards
GET {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/cards
Accept: application/json

###

### Issue a card
POST {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/cards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "<account-id>",
  "cardholderName": "Alice Dupont",
  "type": 0
}

###

### Activate card  (replace <card-id>)
PUT {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/cards/<card-id>/activate

###

### Block card
PUT {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/cards/<card-id>/block

###

### Cancel card
DELETE {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/cards/<card-id>

###

### List all transfers
GET {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/transfers
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a transfer
POST {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": "<from-account-id>",
  "toAccountId": "<to-account-id>",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Monthly rent"
}

###

### Health check
GET {{BankingApi_HostAddress}}/health

###
